title: Welcome!
content:
This is SimpleNotes extension. Easily create, edit, and manage your notes directly in your browser. 

Key features for you:
- Add and modify your notes quickly and effortlessly.
- Backup your notes by exporting them or import from other sources.
- Find note that you need with a simple search function.

 We care about your privacy! All your data stored locally, and won't be accessible online
